sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant API as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Ctrl as odh-model-controller<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Istio as Istio Control Plane<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant IGW as istio-ingressgateway<br/>8445/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Predictor as KServe Predictor Pod<br/>8012/TCP mTLS
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over User,Predictor: Flow 1: InferenceService Reconciliation (KServe Serverless)

    User->>API: Create InferenceService CR
    API->>Ctrl: Watch event notification<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    Ctrl->>API: Read DSCInitialization, ConfigMaps<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Ctrl->>API: Create ServiceMeshMember<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Ctrl->>Istio: Create/Update Gateway server entry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Ctrl->>API: Create OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Ctrl->>API: Create AuthConfig (Authorino)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Ctrl->>API: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Ctrl->>API: Create ServiceMonitor/PodMonitor<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token

    Note over User,Predictor: Runtime Traffic Flow
    User->>Router: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Router->>IGW: TLS Passthrough<br/>8445/TCP HTTPS
    IGW->>Predictor: Inference Request<br/>8012/TCP mTLS (Istio)<br/>Authorino AuthConfig enforced
    Predictor-->>IGW: Prediction Response
    IGW-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over Ctrl,NGC: Flow 2: NIM Account Reconciliation

    API->>Ctrl: NIM Account watch event
    Ctrl->>NGC: Validate API key + fetch catalog<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, NGC API Key (Bearer)
    NGC-->>Ctrl: Model catalog data
    Ctrl->>API: Create NIM catalog ConfigMap<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Ctrl->>API: Create pull Secret<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Ctrl->>API: Create ServingRuntime Templates<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token

    Note over User,Ctrl: Flow 3: Storage Secret Reconciliation

    User->>API: Create data connection Secret<br/>(label: opendatahub.io/managed=true)
    API->>Ctrl: Secret watch event
    Ctrl->>API: List all data connection Secrets<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Ctrl->>API: Create/Update storage-config Secret<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
